ata is used: Your ad topics are based on your recent browsing history, a list of sites you’ve visited using Chrome on this device. How we use this data: Chrome notes topics of interest as you browse. Topic labels are predefined and include things like, Arts & Entertainment, Shopping, and Sports. Later, a site you visit can ask Chrome for a few of your topics (but not your browsing history) to personalize the ads you see. How you can manage your data: Chrome auto-deletes topics that are older than 4 weeks. As you keep browsing, a topic might reappear on the list. You can also block topics you don’t want Chrome to share with sites and turn ad topics off at any time in Chrome settings. Learn more about how Google protects your data in our Privacy Policy."}},"profile":{"avatar_index":26,"background_password_check":{"check_fri_weight":9,"check_interval":"2592000000000","check_mon_weight":8,"check_sat_weight":6,"check_sun_weight":6,"check_thu_weight":9,"check_tue_weight":9,"check_wed_weight":9,"next_check_time":"13374291448040831"},"content_settings":{"did_migrate_adaptive_notification_quieting_to_cpss":true,"disable_quiet_permission_ui_time":{"notifications":"13371920378718548"},"enable_cpss":{"notifications":true},"enable_quiet_permission_ui":{"notifications":false},"enable_quiet_permission_ui_enabling_method":{"notifications":1},"exceptions":{"3pcd_heuristics_grants":{"https://[*.]christitus.com,https://[*.]youtube.com":{"expiration":"13374692225780023","last_modified":"13372100225780031","lifetime":"2592000000000","setting":1},"https://[*.]fiverr.com,https://[*.]youtube.com":{"expiration":"13375397072285127","last_modified":"13372805072285140","lifetime":"2592000000000","setting":1},"https://[*.]github.com,https://[*.]youtube.com":{"expiration":"13375388654778551","last_modified":"13372796654778571","lifetime":"2592000000000","setting":1},"https://[*.]musicalstore2005.com,https://[*.]youtube.com":{"expiration":"13374883657539280","last_modified":"13372291657539290","l